\b  
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 \w Solomon|strong="H8010"\w* ordered \w the|strong="H5921"\w* building \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* Temple\f + \fr 2:1 \ft The words “Temple” and “palace” translate the usual word for “house.”\f* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* honor \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Lord \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* royal palace \w for|strong="H5921"\w* himself.  
