\v 3 Solomon \w sent|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w message|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* Hiram,\f + \fr 2:3 \ft “Hiram,” here spelled “Huram,” also \xt 2:11\ft . (See \xt 1 Kings 5\ft ).\f* \w king|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Tyre, telling \w him|strong="H6440"\w*,  
\v 4 “Please \w do|strong="H3605"\w* \w as|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w did|strong="H1129"\w* \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* father David \w when|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* sent \w him|strong="H3605"\w* cedar timber \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w him|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* \w build|strong="H1129"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w palace|strong="H1004"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* live \w in|strong="H1004"\w*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w*'m \w about|strong="H1004"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* start \w building|strong="H1129"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w Temple|strong="H1004"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* honor \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Lord \w my|strong="H3605"\w* God, dedicated \w to|strong="H1004"\w* \w him|strong="H3605"\w*, \w where|strong="H1004"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H1004"\w* offered sweet-smelling incense, \w where|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* showbread \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H1004"\w* \w always|strong="H3605"\w* \w set|strong="H1129"\w* \w out|strong="H3605"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* rows, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w where|strong="H1004"\w* burnt \w offerings|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H1004"\w* \w made|strong="H1129"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* morning \w and|strong="H1419"\w* evening, \w on|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Sabbaths, \w at|strong="H1004"\w* new moon festivals, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w at|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* feasts \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Lord \w our|strong="H3605"\w* God—\w this|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H1004"\w* \w done|strong="H3605"\w* \w forever|strong="H3605"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* Israel.  
\v 5 \w This|strong="H3588"\w* \w Temple|strong="H1004"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* am \w about|strong="H1004"\w* \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w build|strong="H1129"\w* \w must|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* impressive, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w our|strong="H3588"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w is|strong="H4310"\w* greater \w than|strong="H3808"\w* \w all|strong="H6440"\w* gods.  
\v 6 \w But|strong="H6258"\w* \w who|strong="H3063"\w* \w can|strong="H6213"\w* \w build|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* Temple \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w him|strong="H7971"\w* \w to|strong="H7971"\w* live \w in|strong="H6213"\w*, \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* heavens, \w even|strong="H6213"\w* highest heaven, \w cannot|strong="H3045"\w* contain \w him|strong="H7971"\w*, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w who|strong="H3063"\w* am \w I|strong="H6258"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w* \w I|strong="H6258"\w* \w should|strong="H6213"\w* dare \w to|strong="H7971"\w* \w build|strong="H6213"\w* \w him|strong="H7971"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* house, except \w to|strong="H7971"\w* burn incense \w to|strong="H7971"\w* \w him|strong="H7971"\w*?   
\p
\v 7 \w So|strong="H7971"\w* please \w send|strong="H7971"\w* \w me|strong="H7971"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* master craftsman \w who|strong="H5650"\w* \w is|strong="H2009"\w* skilled \w in|strong="H5650"\w* working \w with|strong="H5973"\w* gold, silver, bronze, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* iron; \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w in|strong="H5650"\w* purple, scarlet, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* blue fabrics. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* must \w also|strong="H3588"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w how|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H7971"\w* engrave, working \w together|strong="H5973"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w my|strong="H3045"\w* expert craftsmen \w from|strong="H3772"\w* Judea \w and|strong="H7971"\w* Jerusalem \w provided|strong="H3045"\w* \w by|strong="H7971"\w* \w my|strong="H3045"\w* father \w David|strong="H7971"\w*.  
\v 8 \w Also|strong="H3588"\w* send \w me|strong="H3588"\w* cedar, cypress, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* algum \w timber|strong="H6086"\w* \w from|strong="H6086"\w* Lebanon, \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* know \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w your|strong="H3588"\w* \w workers|strong="H1129"\w* \w are|strong="H1004"\w* skillful \w in|strong="H1004"\w* cutting \w down|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w trees|strong="H6086"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Lebanon. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* send \w men|strong="H1419"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* help \w your|strong="H3588"\w* \w workers|strong="H1129"\w*  
\v 9 \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w produce|strong="H5414"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* large quantity \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w timber|strong="H6086"\w* because \w the|strong="H5414"\w* Temple \w I|strong="H5414"\w*'m building \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w be|strong="H5414"\w* really large \w and|strong="H6242"\w* very impressive.  
\v 10 \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w pay|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* workers, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* wood-cutters, 20,000 cors \w of|strong="H4428"\w* crushed wheat, 20,000 cors \w of|strong="H4428"\w* barley, 20,000 baths \w of|strong="H4428"\w* wine, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* 20,000 baths \w of|strong="H4428"\w* olive oil.”   
\p
\v 11 \w King|strong="H4428"\w* Hiram \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Tyre responded \w to|strong="H3478"\w* Solomon \w by|strong="H3068"\w* letter: “\w It|strong="H5414"\w*'s \w because|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* loves \w his|strong="H5414"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w* \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*.”  
\v 12 Hiram went \w on|strong="H7971"\w*, “Praise \w the|strong="H3045"\w* Lord, \w the|strong="H3045"\w* \w God|strong="H7971"\w* \w of|strong="H3045"\w* Israel, \w who|strong="H2450"\w* \w made|strong="H3045"\w* \w the|strong="H3045"\w* heavens \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w the|strong="H3045"\w* earth! \w He|strong="H7971"\w* \w has|strong="H3045"\w* given King \w David|strong="H7971"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w wise|strong="H2450"\w* \w son|strong="H2450"\w* \w with|strong="H3045"\w* insight \w and|strong="H7971"\w* understanding \w who|strong="H2450"\w* \w is|strong="H2450"\w* going \w to|strong="H7971"\w* build \w a|strong="H3068"\w* Temple \w for|strong="H7971"\w* \w the|strong="H3045"\w* Lord \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* royal palace \w for|strong="H7971"\w* \w himself|strong="H3045"\w*.   
\p
\v 13 \w I|strong="H5414"\w*'m sending \w you|strong="H5414"\w* Hiram-Abi, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w master|strong="H5414"\w* craftsman \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w knows|strong="H3045"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w understands|strong="H3045"\w* \w what|strong="H3045"\w* \w he|strong="H6213"\w*'s \w doing|strong="H6213"\w*.  
